	<description>	


		The Blind Wizard Of Antreia is a Sound-Novel (It is kind of interactive audio-book). The game consists of sounds only, so it doesn't contain any graphics.
		It is a story of a blind boy who discovers his magical powers. On his way there are many obstacles for him to overcome.	
		Player faces sound riddles, moves around in a world full of sounds, discovers a story.


	</description>
		
